<div class="main-splash">
  <%= image_tag 'shared_secrets_logo.png' %>
</div>

<div class="page-wrapper">
  <div class="container splash-container">
    <%= render 'application/flash' %>
    <div class="well">
      <h1>Connecting you with the money that wins elections.</h1>
      <div class="pure-g">
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
          <p>Working with
            <%= link_to "OpenSecrets.org", "http://opensecrets.org/politicians" %>
            and Twitter, SharedSecrets allows users to find
            representatives from any state and uncover their top campaign contributors and tweet
            their thoughts and discoveries.
          <p>As this is only the beginning of the conversation, users can also interact with other informed
          citizens via posts on any representatives' individual page in order to contribute to
          transparency in our political process.
          <p>Sign up now with Twitter using the link in the upper right hand corner to begin!
          <p>
          <p>
          <p><%= link_to image_tag("opensecrets.gif"), "http://opensecrets.org/politicians" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= render partial: 'application/footer' %>
  </div>
</div>
